\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:12;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:22:\"Métricas para Startup\";s:4:\"text\";s:912:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/84180747\" width=\"298\" height=\"164\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/84180747\">Métricas para Startup - Flavio Alves</a> da <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> no <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> <p>Como saber se seu MVP est&aacute; indo bem? Nesta palestra voc&ecirc; ir&aacute; conhecer algumas formas de rastrear e mensurar o desempenho de sua startup, bem como reagir a esses indicadores. Conhecer&aacute; as m&eacute;tricas e ferramentas mais utilizadas e ouvir&aacute; um pouco da experi&ecirc;ncia de um startupeiro. A palestra se baseia em um estudo sobre m&eacute;tricas para startups que venho trabalhando h&aacute; algum tempo. A palestra tem como refer&ecirc;ncia principal diversas publica&ccedil;&otilde;es de Dave McClure, Eric Ries e Steve Blank.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:13;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:41:\"Should you chuck you the Product Owner!?!\";s:4:\"text\";s:379:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/83274809\" width=\"298\" height=\"164\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/83274809\">Should you chuck out the Product Owner!?! - Nidhi Arora and Karan Nangru</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> \";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:14;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Despertando o potencial humano\";s:4:\"text\";s:531:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/81840416\" width=\"298\" height=\"168\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/81840416\">Despertando o potencial humano - Patrick Kua</a> da <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> no <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> <p>Este foi o keynote de abertura da Agile Brazil 2013, em Brasilia. Patrick Kua nos mostrou sua visão interessante e empolgante do potencial humano e como podemos despertá-lo.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:15;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Patrocínios\";s:4:\"text\";s:387:\"<h3>Bronze</h3>\r\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"140x140-logo-temp\" src=\"http://www.agilebrazil.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/globo.jpg\" style=\"height: 120px;\" /></a>\r\n<p/><p/>\r\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"140x140-logo-temp\" src=\"http://www.agilebrazil.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/rbs.jpg\" style=\"height: 120px;\" /></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Sponsors\";s:4:\"text\";s:387:\"<h3>Bronze</h3>\r\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"140x140-logo-temp\" src=\"http://www.agilebrazil.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/globo.jpg\" style=\"height: 120px;\" /></a>\r\n<p/><p/>\r\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"140x140-logo-temp\" src=\"http://www.agilebrazil.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/rbs.jpg\" style=\"height: 120px;\" /></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Metrics for Startups\";s:4:\"text\";s:807:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/84180747\" width=\"298\" height=\"164\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/84180747\">Metrics for Startups - Flavio Alves</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> <p>How do you know if your MVP is going well? In this talk, you will know some ways of tracking and measuring the performance of your startup as well as how to react to those indicators. You will also know the most popular tools and hear a little of a startuper\'s experience. The talk is based upon a study on metrics for startups on which I\'ve been working for a while. The talk has many publications from Dave McClure, Eric Ries and Steve Blank as references.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:18;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Unlocking the human potential\";s:4:\"text\";s:535:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/81840416\" width=\"298\" height=\"168\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/81840416\">Unlocking the human potential - Patrick Kua</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> <p>This was the opening keynote at Agile Brazil 2013 at Brasilia. Patrick Kua led us through his very interesting and exciting view of the human potential and how we can unleash it.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:19;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"The limbo of latent demand\";s:4:\"text\";s:395:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/88674974\" width=\"298\" height=\"167\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/88674974\">The limbo of latent demand - Al&ecirc; Gomes</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> <p>Historical keynote by Al&ecirc; Gomes</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:20;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:43:\"Você deveria jogar o Product Owner fora!?!\";s:4:\"text\";s:377:\"<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/83274809\" width=\"298\" height=\"164\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/83274809\">Você deveria jogar o Product Owner fora!?! - Nidhi Arora e Karan Nangru</a> da <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/agilebrazil\">Agile Brazil</a> no <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p> \";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}','yes'),(84,'widget_rss','a:0:{}','yes'),(85,'uninstall_plugins','a:1:{s:33:\"posts-to-posts/posts-to-posts.php\";a:2:{i:0;s:11:\"P2P_Storage\";i:1;s:9:\"uninstall\";}}','no'),(8